name: Rick
line: Is that your intention to kill us all?

name: Rick
line: You were always kind to me, Morty. You were the love of my life. You're the reason I come to the surface. You are the reason why I come here. You bring people together.

name: Rick
line: That's pretty harsh, Rick. You came to the dark side to spite us, and you're probably the reason we don't have a home.

name: Agent
line: Yeah, but I mean, I came here to spite you, Morty, so let's not get our hopes up.

name: Rick
line: The trick to the pickle is keeping your balls inside your ass.

name: Rick
line: I came here for the lols. I came to kill you!

name: Agent
line: You came to suck your family?

name: Rick
line: Well, it's possible that we may have been correlating some things that weren't actually related at all.

name: Rick
line: It's possible we may or may have misjudged the extent of your sensitivity, or maybe my love of pickle has been eroded away.

name: Agent
line: Aw, man, man. I really like this pickle.
